title: Hardstyle CD 05-04-08
description:
What a week, lot&#039;s of new tracks!
This week I managed to get quite a lot of new tracks, so this cd is a real pleasure for your ears. I mixed new ones with semi-old ones, and off course a harder track to finish off with. I used Twilight for the second time now, but this is the final version, which is way better then on my second cd.
Here is the list of CD 4:

01.	Brennan Heart - Memento
02.	Dozer - The Curch of the Darkside
03.	D-block & S-te-Fan - Stronger
04.	Hardstyle Mafia vs. Alphaverb - Taking Over
05.	Scope DJ - Twilight
06.	Josh & Wesz - Houze Muzik
07.	G-Town Madness vs. The Viper - Here it Comes (D-Block & S-te-Fan remix)
08.	Deepack - Turnin` da heat up
09.	Josh & Wesz - Fuckin&#039; Posers
10.	Bass Modulators - Indeep (Brainkicker Powered Mix)
11.	Noisecontrollers - Rushroom
12.	Wildstylez - Revenge
13.	Headhunterz - Reloaded Part 2
14.	DJ Mad Dog - Dangerous

Enjoy&Seed
Greetz, Vogelhuisje
